The spec's Twilight Glade is **distance-gated** (≥20 chunks from origin) — this means `assignBiome` needs chunk coords, not just temperature/moisture. Passing `distanceFromOrigin` as a parameter keeps the function pure and testable without knowledge of the noise system.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
